text: Is this about my heater that has still not arrived?
I'm sorry your heater still hasn't arrived.
Would the problem not be on the shippers end?
I just need to verify where the issue has occurred.
Did you pay for the item with the card ending 4686?
What does my card info have to do with this?
It seems there may have been an error on the system.
My order for the heater never went through?
I'm afraid the card details were confused.
I can help verify the card info now?
I would rather do that online then over the phone.
Would you like me to cancel your current order?
"Yes, you can do that since you are already on my account page. "
Could you just confirm the first line of your address please?
You said you had already accessed my account page.
"It's just for security, to confirm I am speaking to NAMESLOTU."
May I ask what your name is NAMESLOTA?
"And what part of Amazon do you work for, Mr. NAMESLOTA? "
